# Bomber Man

> project base cloned from <https://github.com/makinteract/p5js-vite/>

## How To

- [Demo Page](https://web.ntnu.edu.tw/~40971229h/BomberMan/)
  > Portrait mode only

  > Due to financial problem, dockerfile, which used in backend, isn't online yet

- Scripts

### For [backend](./backend/)

```cmd
docker-compose up --build

# new terminal
npm i -g http-server
http-server -c-1 -o ./test.html
```

### For [frontend](./frontend/)

```cmd
npm i
npm run dev

# or
npm run build
cp -r image dist/
```
